{"name":"Mork","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"Chaotic Good","hitDice":"8","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"76 (8d8 + 40)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"20","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"8","chaPoints":"13","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"8","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"","isLair":true,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, Grendelle can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), Grendelle can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The grapple action may not happen two turns in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the green hag's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the green hag's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the green hag dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Pact Magic","desc":"[MON] has made a pact with an elder spirit of the mountain and so can cast spells with a DC [CHA SAVE], and [CHA ATK] to hit. He has taken the invocations _Beast Speech_ and _Book of Ancient secrets_\n\n> At will: _Create Bonfire, Prestidigitation, Mold Earth, Message,\nSpeak with Animals_\n> 2/day: _Expeditious Retreat,\nMirror Image, Invisibility_\n> As Ritual: _Identify, Find Familiar, Comprehend Languages_"},{"name":"Danger Sense","desc":"[MON] has advantage on dexterity saving throws against effects he can see as long as he's not blindned, deafened, or incapacitated."},{"name":"Reckless Attack","desc":"When [MON] makes his first attack he may gain advantage for the rest of the turn. If he does, all attacks against him have advantage."},{"name":"Crusher","desc":"Once per turn, when [MON] hits a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, he can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is large or smaller.\nWhen [MON] scores a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of [MON]'s next turn."},{"name":"Genie's Wrath","desc":"Once during [MON]'s turn, when he hits with an attack roll, he deals +3 extra bludgeoning damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Bottled Respite","desc":"[MON] may retreat back into the spirit phial, after which he is reimprisoned."},{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes three attacks with his claws. (or two with fist if not raging)."},{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D6 + 2] slashing damage."},{"name":"Fist","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR + 1] bludgeoning damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Rage","desc":"3/day. [MON] enters a blind battle rage, attacking one creature until it, or he, dies. An ally's contested Persuasion vs [MON]'s insight can convince him to cease his attack.\nWhile raging, [MON] has advantage on strength checks and saves, resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage, +2 damage to melee attacks, and access to his claws.\nHe also cannot cast or concentrate on spells."},{"name":"Beasthide","desc":"3/day. [MON]'s inner beast emerges as a thick stony carapace covers his forearms and torso.\nGain [1D6 + 6] temporary hit points and +1 AC. (to 20)"}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"animal Handling","stat":"wis"},{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}